create_surface_elements(mesh::Mesh, surface_name::Symbol)




Create a set of surface elements from solid elements.


Notation follow what is defined in ABAQUS. For example, if solid elements are Tet10, surface elements will be Tri6 and they can be used to define boundary conditions.
